name: The Golden Ratio
description:
This is a still from one of my YouTube animations,
https://youtu.be/qd_zFfCyytw

Uses the prompt 'The Golden Ratio'.  Even though it is typically incoherent, the AI is always bold and confident that it is creating exactly what I asked.  And I suppose it's right..

This was made during the time when I was a Patreon supporter of Ryan Murdock - creator of Big Sleep and the whole CLIP & VQGan craze.  To quote him from Discord, "This is one of the best things I've seen in ages".  Praise indeed from a legend!
